<td><p align="left"><font size=+2>F</font>aulkner's fourth novel,

first published on October 7, 1929, is a difficult work that has posed

many problems for both readers and teachers. Because of copyright concerns we are currently not able to offer our hypertext edition of the complete work, but we will continue to offer related materials for exploring the text of the novel, and of augmenting its study, for all levels of readers. In the future we hope to be able to again offer the complete edition.</p>
